verbose_text: Replacement analysis shows that the p.Ser75Pro variant will result in the loss of two hydrogen bonds, one interchain between Ser75 of VAMP2 and Tyr243 of STX1A and one intrachain between Ser75 and Gln71, although the p.Phe77Ser variant introduces a hydrophilic residue in an otherwise hydrophobic region and the p.Glu78Ala variant disrupts the hydrogen bond between Glu78 of VAMP2 and Arg246 of STX1A.
